{"tid":723580,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"向鐘意左3年既女仔告白,結果.....","createTime":"2018-06-30T13:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T08:00:31.000Z","uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"025e78749e10d32edf2c57d395c41caef05d0489","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"差D因為咁而冇左份工<br />\n因為個女仔係工作地方度認識<br />\n但佢未成年仲讀緊書<br />\n對方雖然細自己差唔多10年<br />\n但唔知點解每次工作見到佢時都會好開心<br />\n每次都想下次快D再見到佢...<br />\n<br />\n於是乎半年前膽粗粗ADD左佢<br />\n佢肯ADD我果晚即刻同佢傾左2個鐘<br />\n跟住天光都訓唔著......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後雖然我每次好熱情咁搵佢(FB)<br />\n但都係我講10句佢回1句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知冇機會了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己好唔服氣<br />\n最後我同佢講其實我鐘意你先不斷搵你同你傾計<br />\n點知呢下嚇親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n嚇到佢搵FATHER係佢ACCOUNT度覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識女仔識到我咁火羅連登少有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後仲有更火羅既事超展開........<br />\n估你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落街買D野先上黎再打"},{"pid":"2b79e844d5005299f27f4e7e39731f8c2849f34a","tid":723580,"uid":138138,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"無人想知88"},{"pid":"b10d7c610c2fda9e0fe6fe3c079657d4b9c0d7ca","tid":723580,"uid":104017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0eb7ba8204fa59235e33d04e2a2fc57f437bc6","tid":723580,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:48:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb7ce66dd369df5fdb0e2554dca6369758a67c72","tid":723580,"uid":21423,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d2019a8764fabfa60bdb31c58a3d9a49c7e0672","tid":723580,"uid":60327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係你老世？"},{"pid":"5a364bce5b6cc3e8e088f7395f616888592fb586","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"eb7ce66dd369df5fdb0e2554dca6369758a67c72","tid":723580,"uid":21423,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"犀利......<br />\n咁短時間搵到咁多出黎....<br />\n見另一個POST有位巴打俾你狙擊<br />\n你每次都可以係1樓秒回<br />\n話肥絲係AI我都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae356c4555c526834741fd4dc3062bb2d3fa1e9","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d2019a8764fabfa60bdb31c58a3d9a49c7e0672","tid":723580,"uid":60327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係你老世？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ea4a49ce4b8483f8e6249abf4195226b3cf3c0","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"睇緊波,場波好似幾精彩<br />\n完場先打埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf14d215f57315fd046c9230444f8e995c92d26","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"跟住我當然鳴金收兵啦<br />\n既然另一方冇意思<br />\n始終愛情係相方50+50=100<br />\n我單方面拎足50分仍然係FAIL<br />\n而呢個女仔亦從始消失係我眼前<br />\n佢亦冇再黎我工作既地方......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢段時間我一直耿耿於懷<br />\n呢幾個月都會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時會諗係咪太衝動嚇親人<br />\n應該將份心意收埋起心...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知前日收到經理WSAPP我叫我明天見佢<br />\n想見下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09fda494da9700519ea9b43df54a2d736484dc1","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"咁我開始覺得不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係單野東窗事發<br />\n始終對方係未成年<br />\n<br />\n雖然只係網上聊天吹下水冇做過D乜.....<br />\n睇下樓上既巴打已經係度999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住到左果日<br />\n一入去老闆房坐低<br />\n女老闆同男經理都係度<br />\n<br />\n我諗住呢單野已經半年前<br />\n要投訴應該半年前投訴左<br />\n應該係關其他野事掛.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBOSS:最近收到投訴.....話你走去追人個女....<br />\n我心諗:唔係掛,半年之後都仲要追擊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都完全冇再聯絡佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我心裡面知道人地仲讀緊書<br />\n父母反對係好正常<br />\n但我之前太過優柔寡斷<br />\n錯過左好多機會<br />\n今次難得遇到個好喜歡既<br />\n我唔想因為咁而再錯過多次(求婚大作戰健三模上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住我開始語無倫次.....<br />\n想理性咁抗辯一下<br />\n但事實係我主動搵人在先<br />\n百口莫辯<br />\n<br />\n咁BOSS問我有冇約過人出街<br />\n有冇睇過戲<br />\n我心諗:有鬼咩,個女仔我打10句佢先回我1句<br />\n佢屋企應該係家教好嚴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且最重要既一點係<br />\n我呢刻確信<br />\n佢唔單止唔鐘意我<br />\n仲直情怕左我<br />\n當我係變態佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇埋下文就知點解"},{"pid":"2abaa1522ab1557f81c617c98df8690d2e76ca5a","tid":723580,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"你做過咩黎&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c6aec12c4f49af0620fe54286741ec921f04346e","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"BOSS問我有冇約佢個女仔出過街<br />\n我如實作答<br />\n<br />\nBOSS:你今次好彩,冇同過佢出街,如果唔係後果嚴重.....<br />\n我一臉無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實追女仔追到要俾老闆召見<br />\n已經不是味兒<br />\n分分鐘好大機會係佢父母打黎投訴話要郁我<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得奇怪<br />\n明明係半年前既事<br />\n點解而家先黎投訴呢<br />\n原來佢個女想返黎我地呢邊補<br />\n呢幾個月佢去過其他地方補發覺都係我地呢邊好D<br />\n不過佢FATHER驚我再騷擾佢個女<br />\n所以想報定案同BOSS講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候先知唔怪得BOSS唔係咁嬲<br />\n因為個客去過其他地方發覺都係我呢邊好D<br />\n就算有個痴漢都要做回頭客<br />\n佢係呢方面覺得自豪<br />\n我當然應承就算再見返個女仔,都唔再理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連招呼都唔會同佢打......<br />\n<br />\n最後BOSS仲安慰我:黑色眼睛,就算個女仔幾鐘意你都好,<br />\n但佢未成年,父母始終有權監護,你如果過多2年我地係唔會過問...<br />\n<br />\n我心諗:錯啦,其實唔關其他方面事,係個女仔真心討厭我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後警告信都唔駛收冇事走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n人生第一次認真出手<br />\n換黎咁既經歷,A0之旅仍在繼續....."},{"pid":"a075f8dcffa8206ebdff6e22144a05cd18a4186a","tid":723580,"uid":152023,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"2abaa1522ab1557f81c617c98df8690d2e76ca5a","tid":723580,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"你做過咩黎&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:07:26.000Z","msg":"冇,都係想追個女仔,不過佢未成年<br />\n我工作既地方對呢方面好嚴格<br />\n自己忍唔住去行動搞到灰到土面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我仲未放棄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aa5ef7bf4d1bbd92e19fb98e97bd13d61d04fa","tid":723580,"uid":115412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"3年？仲要未成年？好撚癲喎你<br />\n最多14歲妹妹仔"},{"pid":"11e13f636da2875736f67c4f121156ada82db39f","tid":7